results.title: Live Laugh Love Sign, Live Laugh Love wall decor, Live laugh love wall sign, Slate wall sign, Live Laugh Love Slate sign
results.description:
Live Laugh Love Sign, Live Laugh Love wall decor, Live laugh love wall sign, Slate wall sign, Live Laugh Love Slate sign


This adorable slate sign features a pretty pink flower, a beautiful blue butterfly and two interlacing hearts and the quote, "Live Laugh Love".  

This handmade slate sign is the perfect gift for anyone in your life, including yourself! This meaningful sign reminds us all that life is all about living, laughing, and loving.  This painted Live Laugh Love sign was created using upcycled slate slabs that were originally manufactured in the late 1950s as roofing tiles. 

Slate is a fine grained, foliated and homogenous metamorphic rock derived from an original shale type rock composed of clay for volcanic rock! This means slate can vary in shade from grey, purple, green and cyan, offering you a unique piece of home décor that is truly one of a kind. 

The sign measures 8 inches x 15 inches and weighs approximately 3 lbs 13 oz. 


This Live Laugh Love sign is guaranteed to be handmade by MileyBearDesigns, and comes with two drilled holes for optional hanging and is treated with a waterproof varnish for easy outdoor display.

Please note, the purchase of this handmade sign does not include the display stand.
